Guys let me give list of topics to be covered for an interview for each tools for Devops(You are expected to know this to clear any Devops interview)

AWS
----------
ec2,security group,vpc,nat,subnet,autoscaling,network load balancer, application loadbalancer
s3 bucket,iam,roles,policies,users,cloudwatch,cloudtrail,vpc peering,instance roles,rds


Jenkins
-----------
jenkins custom port,jenksfile,jenkins backup , freestyle job,schedule job,pipeline job,multibranch pipeline
jenkins plugins,jenkins master slave architecture


Docker
----------
dockerfile , dockercompose , docker network types, docker volumes types, docker RUN,CMD,ENTRYPYPOINT ...so on
docker config ,docker multistage build, docker inspect, docker run ... so on



Git
---------------------

git clone , git rebase, git merge, git reset, git revert, git cherry-pick , git push , git fetch , resolving git conflict


Ansible
-------------------
ansible roles, ansible playbook, ansible valut, ansible import and include playbook, ansible config, ansible blocks, ansible seriol, ansible forks
ansible dynamic inventory


Terraform or Cloudformation is MUST
------------------
terraform statefile, terraform plan,apply ..so on
terraform remove add resouce how to
terraform import 

K8s
--------------------
k8s architecture, pv,pvc , role , rolebinding, security, pods , deployments, deameonset, statefulsets
pod affinity, node upgrades,liveness probe , readyness probe .. so on

Linux
-----------------
load avg,slow issue, filesystem full, user administration, fs management
security, package management
patching,kernel upgrades and so on


Scripting( Shell or Python)
------------------
functions,forloop,whileloop,variables,if else


Build tools(Maven)
-------------
how many stages in maven builds, how to see logs, how to deploy , commands
